Omaha.Elmwood Tower: The Elmwood Tower (formerly known as the Masonic Manor) is a high-rise residential building located at 801 South 52nd Street in midtown Omaha, Nebraska. Completed in 1963, the Elmwood Tower is a 320-ft (98-m) high-rise building, rising to 21 stories. It is currently the third tallest skyscraper in Omaha behind First National Bank Tower and Woodmen Tower.
